# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore for Wallace Home & Property Services (wallacehps-site)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Purpose:
#   This repository hosts the static website and AI assistant links for
#   Wallace Home & Property Services, a Tallahassee-based handyman and
#   home maintenance company. This file ensures that unnecessary system
#   files, local cache data, or development artifacts are not uploaded
#   to GitHub, keeping the repo clean and professional.
#
# Notes:
#   - This site is deployed through GitHub Pages using index.html.
#   - Only web assets (HTML, CSS, JS, images, README, LICENSE) should be tracked.
#   - Add new ignore rules here if local build tools or generators are added later.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# OS and editor clutter
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# Backup and temp files
*.bak
*.tmp

# Optional: Node or web bundler folders (if used in the future)
node_modules/
dist/
.env

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# End of file
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
